{"type":"assistant","content":"---\n\n## Implementation Complete\n\n**Change:** calculator-keyboard-navigation\n**Schema:** spec-driven\n**Progress:** 18/18 tasks complete ✓\n\n### Completed This Session\n\n**1. Display Element Migration**\n- [x] 1.1 Replaced `<div class=\"display\">` with `<input type=\"text\" class=\"display\">` (value/spellcheck/autocomplete attrs set)\n- [x] 1.2 Added `outline: none; width: 100%` to `.display` CSS to strip browser input chrome while keeping the visual box styling\n- [x] 1.3 Added `#display { caret-color: transparent; }` + `#display:focus { caret-color: auto; }` for caret visibility management\n- [x] 1.4 `updateDisplay()` now sets `display.value` (with cursor position preservation via `setSelectionRange`)\n- [x] 1.5 `input` event listener re-syncs `display.value` from `calc.currentInput` to block direct edits\n\n**2. Cursor-Aware Digit Insertion**\n- [x] 2.1 `calc.startNewEntry(digit)` — sets `waitingForOperand = true`, calls `inputDigit`, then `display.focus()`\n- [x] 2.2 `inputDigit` — when display is focused, inserts digit at `selectionStart` within `currentInput` and restores cursor\n- [x] 2.3 `inputDecimal` — when display is focused, inserts `.` at cursor position (if no decimal already present)\n\n**3. Revised Keydown Guard and Routing**\n- [x] 3.1 Guard now suppresses only for `INPUT` (not the display) / `TEXTAREA` / `SELECT` — buttons no longer blocked\n- [x] 3.2–3.3 Button + digit/`.` → `calc.startNewEntry()`, return\n- [x] 3.4 Button + `=`/`Enter` → return early, letting the browser's native button click fire\n- [x] 3.5 Button + operator → falls through to global operator handler\n\n**4. Spatial Button Navigation**\n- [x] 4.1 `getFocusableButtons()` filters out `disabled`, `hidden`, and `visibility:hidden` buttons\n- [x] 4.2 `navigateButtons(direction)` uses `getBoundingClientRect()` centers and Euclidean distance to pick the nearest candidate\n- [x] 4.3 Arrow keys on a focused button → `navigateButtons()` + `preventDefault`\n- [x] 4.4 `ArrowLeft`/`ArrowRight` on display → not intercepted (native cursor movement)\n- [x] 4.5 `ArrowUp`/`ArrowDown` on display → `navigateButtons()` to nearest button above/below + `preventDefault`\n\nAll tasks complete! Ready to archive this change with `/opsx:archive calculator-keyboard-navigation`.","workflow_id":"41f7e207f666f675888ab5719085d332","ts":"2026-04-20T13:19:19.673Z"}
